articles.title: Myanmar junta 'extremely disappointed' over leader's exclusion from ASEAN summit - CNN
articles.description: Myanmar's military junta said Saturday it was "extremely disappointed" with a decision by Southeast Asian foreign ministers to exclude its leader Min Aung Hlaing from an upcoming summit.
